item.title: Changelog
item.description: Changelog # All notable changes to this project are documented in this page. The format is based on Keep a Changelog. 1.3.3 - 2023-08-21 # Changed # BlendShape Weight mismatch warning is now build-time warning instad of validate time warning #359 Thanks to FreeseBlendShape by TraceAndOptimize, most pre-build this warning is false positive. So this warning is moved to build-time only. Fixed # ClearEndpointPosition is not applied for non-first PhysBones on the GameObject #357 Incompatbile with Reload Scene disabaled #358 1.
